{"tid":1513031,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貴婦12歲 琴日離開左我","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T06:41:43.000Z","uid":100331,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc249e82e6e23e20c3e672dee849e73278f2865b","tid":1513031,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"我隻肥豬7月慶祝完12歲生日<br />\n一直都好乖乖<br />\n一直都精精神神<br />\n但有啲野 突然發生左<br />\n腎衰竭 唔食唔飲唔痾<br />\n<br />\n就咁走左 所有回憶歷歷在目<br />\n我好掛住佢<br />\n星期六要火化<br />\n我要抱咩心情去 <br />\n<br />\n我唔想面前喱一切"},{"pid":"106d8208addc21e57521cb6c9e473c6d60826aa9","tid":1513031,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:53:05.000Z","msg":"rip<br />\n加油!"},{"pid":"b12bc5e21eaff4009d34e8366d077c94d5488a3d","tid":1513031,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5741bd1357a519d02b748bdaf6e989b441da444a","tid":1513031,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:53:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我隻貓走嗰陣 喊到世界末日咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02051b785907cce41af26b18650aa09b10ad6c2c","tid":1513031,"uid":281342,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCrFNAj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCrFNAj.jpg&h=0b132a02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAK8b10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAK8b10.jpg&h=054ab481&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nRZiG0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nRZiG0.jpg&h=372ddf78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTuj28F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTuj28F.jpg&h=f01dee5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0PLYG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0PLYG1.jpg&h=8e59ba0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21aecb9eb876827e889ec33383114e042e3348b7","tid":1513031,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"去左外面讀書讀半年 6月返香港<br />\n以為無野再分開我地<br />\n<br />\n6-8月對香港人黎講 係好攰既2個月<br />\n我都好攰<br />\n<br />\n但無諗過 個天會係喱一刻 帶走佢<br />\n<br />\n好突然 我最親既人 比老豆老母更親<br />\n係我個女 係我最愛最錫既女<br />\n<br />\n點解要咁對媽咪 我好掛住你"},{"pid":"01924a08501d9507389054f41390dc347f3cd178","tid":1513031,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:56:33.000Z","msg":"喊左好耐 喊到唔想再喊<br />\n但一諗到佢 又繼續喊 <br />\n好攰啊 火化個一日<br />\n我要點樣面前 <br />\n<br />\n我唔知"},{"pid":"38ad697a9ce5930465b4f7e5eb70f800f882fec7","tid":1513031,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:56:48.000Z","msg":"你可唔可以返返黎"},{"pid":"8db7bb552eaa76709bb7a7508b9631cd1484b3f6","tid":1513031,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:58:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9d17408a22baf79ab754f4f9a5e27767270419","tid":1513031,"uid":140218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"狗狗唔痛喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n節哀, 終有一日會喺彩虹橋再見"},{"pid":"9c72fd929ce5c5bb675737896399b4e9e3be39ff","tid":1513031,"uid":97340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"佢始終會早走過你<br />\n佢生前開心去得舒服<br />\n同埋佢永遠响你心入面佔一席位<br />\n已經係佢最大既幸福<br />\n<br />\nps. 屋企隻魔天使都年頭去左"},{"pid":"f9280f7668eb5a7a266b74cbbeec5498fcf57e02","tid":1513031,"uid":307725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n雖然肉體唔可以繼續陪住你<br />\n但你同狗狗既回憶會一齊陪住你<br />\n只係用左另一個方式<br />\n我隻貴婦17年走左<br />\n有時諗起佢都會喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油﹐佢而12年有你錫已經好幸福"},{"pid":"421ae8781ac4d8114fab8957585219bba526e1c1","tid":1513031,"uid":283431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"節哀順變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗狗上咗天堂 佢會永遠開開心心"},{"pid":"f7537d6261392ce1968a1513feb294e8388eca51","tid":1513031,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"302eadd069333938f1b9a59b9820031e16bba681","tid":1513031,"uid":304352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7537d6261392ce1968a1513feb294e8388eca51","tid":1513031,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T07:49:11.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"仆街啦你"},{"pid":"50145a0fc7736cad15dd42164065636157bca915","tid":1513031,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"要振作"}]}